\c 123 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 123\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Harka Waaqayyoo Eeggachuu (Weedduu ittiin ol ba'an)
\m \bd 1\bd* Ati bantiiwwan waaqaa keessa teessoo kee irra waan jirtuuf, iji koo ol gara kee in ilaala.
\m \bd 2\bd* Iji hojjetootaa, harka isa isaan hojjechiifatuu, iji hojjettuu, harka ishee ishee hojjechiifattuu in eeggata; akkasuma immoo hamma Waaqayyo gooftaan keenya araara nutti argisiisutti, iji keenya gara isaa in ilaala.
\m \bd 3\bd* Araara nutti argisiisi, yaa Waaqayyo, araara nutti argisiisi! Nu'oo salphina quufnee nu irraa hafeera.
\m \bd 4\bd* Namummaan keenya ceephoo warra quufoo, isa warri of gurguddisan nu salphisanis baay'isee quufeera.
\b 
